data.description: Welcome to the spacious, well-designed and coveted Cali floor plan. This single-story home offers both comfort and style, making it an ideal choice for families and individuals alike. As you step into this home, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting living space. The home  features four bedrooms, providing plenty of room for a growing family, a home office, or guest rooms. The master suite is a true retreat with ample space, a walk-in closet, and a private en-suite bathroom featuring double sinks and a separate shower. The heart of the home is the open-concept living area that seamlessly connects the family room, kitchen, and dining area. This design is perfect for those who love to entertain or for keeping an eye on the family while preparing meals. The modern kitchen is equipped with quality appliances, plenty of counter space, and a convenient island, making it a functional and stylish focal point of the home. Located in Willow Bend, this home is part of a vibrant community with amenities such as a playground, pool and clubhouse. Its prime location offers easy access to US-27, schools, shopping, restaurants and amusement parks. Call now for your showing appointment!
